xquery version "1.0";
(:~ Format the resource.
 : Required parameters:
 :  to= format
 :  output= group
 :  style=  location of style file
 :
 : Method: POST
 : Status:
 : 	202 Accepted, request is queued for processing
 :	401, 403 Authentication
 :	404 Bad format 
 : Returns Location header
 :
